// IntroString :
"P2135438632" "Marshal Blitz and his Rogue Arachnos are of no concern to you - they're just a group that presents an opportunity. <br><br> If anyone manages to stop them, it'll either mean Arachnos has more power to oversee your actions, or that Longbow will have a few more soldiers to spare to throw at you. Neither of those is something you're too willing to let slide. <br><br> You can use some technology you've picked up in the past to fake a signal to Longbow regarding the location of the base. Then it's just a matter of dealing with whoever shows up, though you can bet they'll be sending a decent force to try to save their soldiers."
// AcceptString :
"P1574928188" "Trap Longbow and defeat their rescue squad!"
// SendOffString :
"P767920977" "You head off towards an abandoned Arachnos base. You're not too sure who might be currently residing in there, but you'll be sure to kick them out to get your plans set in motion. It's the least you could do to set up a proper welcome for Longbow."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3995155684" "Trick Longbow!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P759125886" "Hopefully Longbow is sending some big-named heroes after these prisoners. That'll make this interesting, at least."
// TaskTitle :
"P751426736" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>ATTENTION! SLAVES OF ARACHNOS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

