// Clue Name :
"P3994103453" "Computer Codes"
// DetailString :
"P3067118805" "It seems the Rogue Arachnos were more intent on beating the information out of the scientist than simply searching him. You were able to swipe his key card, which will give you access to the Arachnos computers - once everything else is handled."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - MarshalBlitzMessage 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4165432801" "Marshal Blitz's Threat"
// DetailString :
"P612595395" "You defeated the Demolitions Expert, who was speaking with Marshal Blitz. You overheard the following on the communicator upon his defeat: <br><br><color Cadetblue> So, {HeroName}. You're trying to stop me, are you? I assume with the defeat of Dempsey that the base is no longer in danger. But it doesn't matter. We're more than you can imagine, and eventually we will gain control of the Isles. When we do, you'll be the first to be taken out. Mark my words."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3070988094" "The operatives in Arachnos are already bloodthirsty as it is - at least there are the Arbiters there to keep them in check. Marshal Blitz is a loose cannon and bad for business in the Isles. Any headway he makes isn't going to be good for anyone - not even those deluded Arachnos that follow him. <br><br> Someone needs to stop him from destroying that base and gaining even more of a foothold within the Isles. <br><br> Not for <i>free</i>, of course."
// AcceptString :
"P800744050" "Stop the Rogue Arachnos and take the Arachnos data."
// SendOffString :
"P2631932125" "You head off to the Arachnos base in question to stop Blitz and his operations. In the hope of getting a good amount of information out of it for yourself, of course."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1759597493" "Stop the Rogue Arachnos!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4146153801" "Given all the various experiments Arachnos is working on, it wouldn't be surprising to find information on any of the really big ones here."
// TaskTitle :
"P2890359919" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>ATTENTION! SLAVES OF ARACHNOS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2932630952" "You enter the base to see a slew of Longbow prisoners at your feet. It looks like Blitz and his men don't care about waiting to see if their demands are met."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3290494930" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>ATTENTION! SLAVES OF ARACHNOS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You stopped Marshal Blitz and his mad scheme to blow up an Arachnos base. You made off with precious information, the Rogue Arachnos were pushed back, and everyone got back all of their proper operatives. Everybody wins. Except for Blitz."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4142815171" "Yes sir, we've taken out the Longbow prisoners. They won't be sending any signals today."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1436323287" "Hold on, sir, we have an intruder!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3489152553" "For Marshal Blitz! For the downfall of Arachnos!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3481028041" "Do you think this is right? I mean, that Blitz is actually better than Recluse?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P151374735" "Even if it means fighting {HeroName}...this is what I've chosen!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P16161644" "It's too late to second-guess him now. This is the only option we have left."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2520862944" "Demolitions Expert Dempsey"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2468905211" "Operative Dempsey is one of the higher ups within the Rogue Arachnos. He is fully trained as a demolitions expert and is frequently used by Blitz to carry out his plans. "
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P642698592" "Yes sir. It's all set and waiting for your signal."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1084097189" "Hold on, we've got some problems! It's {HeroName}, sir!"

