"P923653479" "I saw a cargo ship on fire off in the distance the other day. I wonder what that was all about?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_03 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SkyDragon 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2588668012" "Sky Dragon's Possession"
// DetailString :
"P1020770129" "You fought and defeated the hero Sky Dragon in the caverns beneath St. Martial, though as he fell his body vanished in a cloud of purple smoke. The Circle must have performed one of their rituals on him - either they've forced one of their spirits into his body with their thorns or a mage is possessing him. However, you're unable to investigate further due to his vanishing and the lack of other clues."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ClueRitual 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1175056147" "The Circle Ritual"
// DetailString :
"P2032367596" "You found the ritual that the Circle used to trap the Legacy Chain in the spirit world - along with a way to free them."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3121927622" "While the Legacy Chain might not be at the top of your list of concerns, the fact that Longbow are currently in negotiations with the Circle to release them can work towards your benefit. It would be a simple matter of attacking the Circle, stealing the incantation to release the Legacy Chain, then selling it off to Longbow. <br><br>Longbow might not appreciate that you're still <i>selling</i> this to them - in fact they certainly won't appreciate it - but it'll make you some money and they'll get those Legacy Chain back."
// AcceptString :
"P3421580764" "Sell the key to release the Legacy Chain!"
// SendOffString :
"P479657181" "The Circle of Thorns lair seems to be in an underground cavern in St. Martial - different than their usual stomping grounds of Oranbega. Not that it's a problem, of course."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1748571882" "Sell the Legacy Chain's Fates"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3802460379" "If only more members of the Circle did business outside of Oranbega."
// TaskTitle :
"P25045656" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Rather Persistent Spirit</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3803202309" "The Circle are preparing to move out to meet Longbow in the negotiations. Well, at least that's what they think."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1324639276" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Rather Persistent Spirit</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You leave the cavern and see your contact from Longbow waiting for you. You make the deal with the man, who quickly walks off afterwards. The briefcase of money given to you has some weight to it - opening it up, you see a good amount of money inside. Longbow pays well when they want one of their own allies back. A good thing to remember."
// Script Variable VICTIM_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1888845878" "Ancestor Spirit"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P1779702304" "Interesting...begin the process of tearing the spirit apart."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P2634098262" "The Tsoo will not take this lightly!"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_ATTACK_TEXT :
"P2876560396" "{HeroName}, is it? This should prove interesting."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_HOSTILE_TEXT :
"P2395934464" "Eerrgh!"
// Script Variable VICTIM_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1728819222" "Crey Agent"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P3108225338" "Probe his mind. Find out Crey's secrets."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P3751378039" "Get out of my head..."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_ATTACK_TEXT :
"P3804099900" "How unfortunate. {HeroName}."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_HOSTILE_TEXT :
"P1205736517" "No one can know I was here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2070558533" "Sky Dragon"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4209945158" "Sky Dragon is master of a mystical martial art known only to a few Eastern sorcerers. He has come to Paragon city to defeat villainy in all its forms.<br><br>However, he has been captured and tortured by the Circle of Thorns, his once bright mind corrupted by the mages who sought to learn his secrets. His mind is no longer his own - it is now controlled by the Circle."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P346861602" "This man's body will do just nicely. Now, to put it to use..."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1667401588" "Ah, {HeroName}. You shall be the first that I test this man's skills on. Prepare yourself!"

