// IntroString :
"P212546004" "If the Rogue Isles Police think you're just going to sit around while yet <i>another</i> organization bent on 'policing' the Isles tries to get organized, they have another thing coming to them. It's not that they would actually be able to stop any of your plans, but it certaintly won't help having to consider a new thorn from the many that can be in your side. <br><br>Striking down the RIP while they're all gathered will send a clear message to them - you're not welcome in {HeroName}'s town."
// AcceptString :
"P625783276" "Disrupt the RIP Convention!"
// SendOffString :
"P1286617246" "It'll be as simple as taking down the heads of the RIP, along with scaring a few of the potential recruits while you're there."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P958389308" "Attack the RIP Convention!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4054886986" "There shouldn't be a shortage of donuts at the convention, at least."
// TaskTitle :
"P860498817" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The RIP Wants YOU!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2976474363" "The floor of the office building is littered with promotional fliers for the Rogue Isles Police."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2529273851" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The RIP Wants YOU!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You don't think this is how the RIP imagined their convention ending. Savage Siren will also be hurting pretty badly after that encounter - maybe that'll show her that she's out of her league."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3705494427" "RIP Recruit"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2992867276" "This man seems to be interested in working for the RIP."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3619075238" "Hrm...I don't know...<em t=5> Huh, every single day?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2810870156" "Ahh! {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1754005314" "There are many benefits to joining the RIP! <em t=3> Our insurance plan is second to none, and you'll love every day of your work."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3073603236" "Now just sit back and see how we deal with problems like {HeroName}!"
