"P2761189074" "One piece of information remains!"
// InteractBeginString :
"P3528387643" "You access the computer."
// InteractCompleteString :
"P977785347" "You finish accessing the computer."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
