"P3788806010" "Looks like we've got a buzzkill! {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P210742465" "Oh, Vivacious was SO right in telling us to come here - I'm having an absolute BLAST!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
