// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P986178500" "Oh my! It's {HeroName}! What fun this will be!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1079637934" "Oh, of course, she should be far into the sewers by now."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1492068588" "Watch out for any Arachnoids!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2406661834" "Don't be ridiculous! There aren't any Arachnoids near here."
