"P2540150823" "I saw that special on WSPDR about the RIP. Gave me the chills! How did they find out about that?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL6-7_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SerumResult 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1708657993" "Longbow Base Chaos"
// DetailString :
"P1976100178" "When you activated the serum, the entire Longbow base shook from the large explosion. This is your chance to sweep in and take down the Longbow commander in charge before they can gain control over the situation."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1591437022" "Crey's problem has always been that they're too cautious about utilizing impressive technology right away. This formula for 'exploding water' is something that could be extremely useful, when used in the right hands. Your hands, to be specific. <br><br> One of Longbow's main bases in the Rogue Isles is within Agincourt. The base has its own supply of water - pumped out through various generators deep beneath the base. <br><br> If you could insert the formula into the stream then activate it, it would cripple one of Longbow's main resources in the Isles."
// AcceptString :
"P3937825798" "Use Crey's formula to cripple Longbow!"
// SendOffString :
"P4156639705" "Swiping the formula from Crey is something you can do on the way there, if they're performing their experiments within Nerva as well. Then it's simple setting Longbow up to knock them down."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1535921004" "Cripple Longbow in Agincourt!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1849893057" "It's always best to hit your enemies where they'll hurt the most - their precious resources."
// TaskTitle :
"P277922564" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Syringe Oozing Goo</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1634424384" "It was easy enough to steal the serum Crey was using from the scientists in Nerva - the fools thought no one would know where they were. Now it's just a matter of using it to cause some chaos in this Longbow base."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2818866543" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Syringe Oozing Goo</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step out from the ruined Longbow base. It'll take them a long time to recover - time which they won't be spending monitoring any of your activities within the Isles. This would be the perfect time to start getting any plans of yours into motion!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1625818007" "Sometimes the hum of the generators makes me so sleepy. You know what I mean? <em t=3> ...that was uncalled for."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3071183656" "I do, your talking makes me tired a lot also."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2475657856" "It's {HeroName}! Look alive!"

