// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P58427961" "Commander Montagne is a decorated officer of Longbow, though after suffering serious injuries during the second Rikti War, he was placed on guard duty for the water supply in Agincourt, under the belief he wouldn't see much action. Longbow was wrong."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
