// RandomFameString :
"P2089919530" "I saw a bunch of Longbow over in Nerva were freaking out at the sight of water. What could've caused them to act like that?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - KeyCard 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3489571326" "Crey Key Card"
// DetailString :
"P2036925196" "You found this key card on Crey's lead researcher. It will give you access to their systems, allowing you to free any people - or creatures - that Crey is experimenting on. They might come in handy, if you want to really stick it to Crey. It would just be a matter of finding the proper console to use it on."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3359520370" "Does Crey really think they can get away with going against both Arachnos and Longbow? Something like this could cause some serious chaos in the Rogue Isles - Longbow will be scouring it for signs of Crey activity, Arachnos will be doing whatever it takes to put Crey down. And when those two groups meet...well, let's just say the idea of doing business in a black market will be out the window when an all out war is going on right behind you. <br><br> Someone needs to step up and stop this - while also making a profit. Which shouldn't be too hard to do, given the market you deal in."
// AcceptString :
"P2664647408" "Find evidence against Crey to sell to Arachnos!"
// SendOffString :
"P2657450064" "You head off to one of Crey's main labs in Nerva Archipelago. You'll have to make sure to destroy the source of the serum so it can't be used, then hack Crey's computers in order to retrieve physical data regarding what exactly they were planning."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3501153933" "Obtain Evidence Against Crey!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P362711429" "There's no telling what experiments Crey might be brewing down in those labs - you had better be careful."
// TaskTitle :
"P1618430693" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Syringe Oozing Goo</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2699773034" "There are some odd marks along the walls of this lab - it looks like Crey does more than just chemical research here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3689983893" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Syringe Oozing Goo</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You almost had to turn down all of the offers that Arachnos was making for information on Crey. You spoke with an Operative Vargas, who was extremely eager to pay whatever you requested for the information. Now it's just a matter of sitting back and watching Arachnos deal with Crey."
// Script Variable OBJECT_DISPLAYNAME :
"P359189065" "Crey Serum"
// Script Variable ACTOR_GUARDING_DIALOG :
"P2827443718" "We need to get the serum moving now. That team is waiting for it out in Primerva."
// Script Variable ACTOR2_GUARDING_DIALOG :
"P97020217" "I don't feel good about this... Moving this out in plain sight? What if one of those Destined Ones attack us?"
// Script Variable ACTOR_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3189936079" "We'll worry about that after we take care of {HeroName}!"

