// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL6-7_Task_06 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P4197352246" "I-i-it's you...{HeroName}...! S-stop right there...! I swear I'll shoot...I-I swear! <br><br><color Orange>Looks like Hero Corps was hired out to guard this bank during the chaos. The agent is absolutely terrified - he is shaking so much that the gun in his hands looks like it's going to fall apart from the rattling."
// Answer Text :
"P3473997230" "You swear you'll shoot? Really? Go for it."
// Answer Text :
"P4114738049" "Now why would you want to shoot me?"
// Answer Text :
"P1841249402" "I don't have time for this. Out of my way!"
// Answer Text :
"P632131380" "I'll be back to handle you."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P2390026424" "I...I...! <br><br><color Orange>The guard drops his gun in a panic, looking up to you."
// Answer Text :
"P4191686759" "This is the part when you run in fear before I beat you."
// Answer Text :
"P3484655416" "Bad move. (Take down the guard)"
// Page RuninFear Text :
"P3110074575" "<color Orange>The guard runs for his life with a terrified 'Thank you' for allowing him to go unharmed."
// Answer Text :
"P3566142116" "Now for the money in the vault..."
// Page Guardtakedown Text :
"P2956017713" "<color Orange>The guard lets out a scream, which you quickly <color red>silence</color>."
// Answer Text :
"P3800908276" "Hmph. Now for the vault."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P795632278" "B-because you're here to rob the bank! That's why!"
// Answer Text :
"P2819067784" "Honestly, is that a good reason to shoot someone like me?"
// Answer Text :
"P4171555101" "When you say it like that, I don't have any choice! (Attack)"
// Page GoodReason Text :
"P1925013324" "I...it is! This is my job you know!"
// Answer Text :
"P3717198" "Look around you. Everyone's gone. Why don't you just run along before you get hurt?"
// Page RunAlong Text :
"P3195599115" "<color orange> The guard slowly lowers his gun, looking at you in a mixture of fear and awe."
// Answer Text :
"P3675194466" "Don't think of this as mercy, you're just too...beneath me to deal with."
// Page BeneathMe Text :
"P3024437744" "<color Orange>The guard sprints out of the door, almost stumbling over himself."
// Answer Text :
"P2351972062" "Such ridiculous guards. Now for the vault."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2398223566" "<color orange>The guard leaps forward to attack, but you easily take him down. He was never a threat in the first place."
// Answer Text :
"P3663852510" "Time to get my prize in the vault."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2779683169" "Why not rob the bank in Founder's Falls? Everyone there currently seems preoccupied with whatever is happening in that Arachnos base - and from the sound of it, there wouldn't be too much chaos you could add to the whole mess. <br><br> Getting into Founder's will be simple if you use the system of canals they have set up. Then it will just be a matter of walking into that bank and taking what you want - there's a strong possibility it might not even be guarded!"
// AcceptString :
"P3418153962" "Rob the bank in Founder's Falls!"
// SendOffString :
"P1764162187" "You head off towards Founder's Falls. Perhaps you should time this to see just how fast you can rob this bank."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3738060027" "Rob the Founder's Falls Bank!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3657500926" "The part with the Council being ambushed by 5th Column might have been the only surprising part of that entire event."
// TaskTitle :
"P676587538" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Sounds of Utter Chaos</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3140588119" "Just as you thought. Totally empty. Everyone must be either fighting in that base or gawking at the fighting going on there. Time to make your move."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4239323449" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Sounds of Utter Chaos</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Things got a bit hairy back there in the bank, but it was nothing you couldn't handle. You made off with a good payment for the day - even if it was at the cost of the college savings funds of those children in Founder's Falls."
