"P4102824337" "<shout>Man, why does Miss Francine put us on boring GUARD duty of some stupid bank?!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4123087577" "<shout>It's supposed to teach us to take initiative to help people, or something."
