"P3097926157" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>8Uff00N's Left Hand</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You leave the warehouse with the charity event in ruins. You'd feel bad for whoever those items were supposed to go to - if you cared, that is."
