"P2925585327" "That shock would be {HeroName}! <em t=2> ...wait, {HeroName}? I'm shocked too!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P580734433" "Whew, thanks {HeroName}. <em t=2> Say, if you're not gonna hand me my head, why don't we work together on this thing? <em t=3> It'll be FUN! I'll follow you!"
