"P4107215131" "Longbow Officer"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3624060097" "The bravest of the brave, and those who have proven their ability to lead as well as fight, are promoted to officers. They are then given special bio-enhancers that make them far stronger than normal men, as well as energy-absorbing suits that offer great protection against most forms of damage."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
