// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4098905360" "Payment is payment, even if it means going after another villain within the Rogue Isles. Doc Buzzsaw has been known to have a very random assortment of items lying about - getting access to this collection will lead to something that will at least be profitable. <br><br> It's just a matter of tracking down Shock Treatment before anyone else manages to get her."
// AcceptString :
"P2642088736" "Capture Shock Treatment before anyone else can!"
// SendOffString :
"P1595823405" "Longbow will be holding the charity event that Shock Treatment is crashing in Nerva, though you doubt it'll be in one piece by the time you get there."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2738172246" "Capture Shock Treatment!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P324248599" "You doubt this would be as easy as finding Shock Treatment before anyone else does."
// TaskTitle :
"P3253722484" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>8Uff00N's Left Hand</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2280492245" "The charity event seems to be in a wreck! Shock Treatment is probably at the center of this - amidst everyone else trying to find her."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1321294026" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>8Uff00N's Left Hand</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Almost as if she knew when you would be done, you exit to see Doc Buzzsaw standing in front of you, holding her hand out. You hand over Shock Treatment and Doc Buzzsaw kicks over a large chest beside her. Opening up, you see various bits of interesting technology - all of it usable or sellable."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1002638199" "Look for Shockie dears, I'm sure we'll find her in here somewhere!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1973844483" "Joining in the hunt, {HeroName}? Oh, I don't think so.  We can't have that!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P359195489" "Galaxy Archon"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P456660088" "Let's just hurry up and find this woman. I need some serious money from this."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P823678897" "Just what I needed. This was supposed to be simple! SIMPLE!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1831792935" "The Captain said we'd be paid real well for finding this woman."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2901961257" "I hope so. I'm missing out on today's fighting ring at Totting's house."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1543485385" "Just when I thought this might've been easy!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1702795532" "You Carnival have been an annoyance for far too long. We have the girl, now give up."
// Script Variable FIGHTER_TWO_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P502700607" "Really, darling, what are you going to do with that payment? We'll use it MUCH better than you!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P14689086" "You clowns freak me out! Go back to wherever you came from!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_TWO_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3625997516" "Mmmhmmhmhm...you're all so crass! It's almost beneath us to deal with you, but we shall!"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P3225789374" "We've got you now, Shock Treatment. No one will be able to save you."
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P4233512366" "Errrrgh! Let me GO!"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_SACRIFICER_ATTACK_TEXT :
"P3858297676" "It's {HeroName}?! Stay away. We will use Buzzsaw's reward to fight the Rikti!"
// Script Variable SACRIFICE_VICTIM_HOSTILE_TEXT :
