// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P167435399" "What's going on here?! <em t=2> {HeroName}'s work...I knew the day would come when I would have to put you down."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2904508614" "You don't know who you're dealing with, {HeroName}. I've eaten punks like you for breakfast."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2867729307" "That the best you've got?! I've gone into the heart of the Netherworld and survived! You've got nothing!"
