// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3142682530" "St. Martial has already been devastated enough by the Wailers - the entire eastern portion of the island is evidence enough. If they're somehow working with the Devouring Earth, it can only spell trouble for the rest of St. Martial - it could soon turn the entire island, save for the Giza, into a wasteland! <br><br> How exactly are you going to do business on an island where the only safe place to go is always watched over by the Family? <br><br> A situation like this demands someone to take action - especially when there's money involved."
// AcceptString :
"P2159327462" "Destroy the alliance between the Wailers and the Devouring Earth!"
// SendOffString :
"P1790643827" "You'll have to work fast to get into that office and see whatever it is that is uniting the two groups - then destroy it."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3736675501" "Save St. Martial for the right price!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P668956346" "St. Martial will be in a lot of trouble if the Wailers somehow teach the Devouring Earth to sing."
// TaskTitle :
"P455278672" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Demonic Pink Slip</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1526905371" "The walls in this office are littered with strange carvings done by the Wailers. They've marked their territory here with the Devouring Earth. Time to change that."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3994387493" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Demonic Pink Slip</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Whatever was holding together the Devouring Earth and Wailers was shattered upon Mangle's defeat. Something must have happened to this deviant to really drive him off the deep end. Though at the end of the day, does it really matter? With the threat gone, you received a healthy payment from Hardcase and the satisfaction of knowing it's still business as usual in St. Martial."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P4260422440" "Silent Blade"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3557696553" "Ergh! Let me pass you beasts! Someone needs to stop this!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1018145891" "{HeroName}? Give me a hand here!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4176745507" "Graaaagh!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1892819118" "Thank you. <em t=2> I do not know what you have heard of me, but regardless, I am here to stop these creatures from destroying the Martial. <em t=2> I do this not for the reward from Hardcase, but simply because the Martial is my home, and I shall fight for it if it comes to it. <em t=2> Let us go."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - SilentBlade 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2201196672" "Mangle's gonna mangle the Martial!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P415709629" "{HeroName}! We'll boogie down over your bloody corpse!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P820532940" "Ooo! Aaa! Boogie oogie!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2996073972" "Devour you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P886151376" "Mangle"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2623564755" "Mangle was an unwilling attraction for a roaming freak show, but the chains couldn't contain his fury forever. Once freed, he waited in the shadows to repay his captors' kindness with blood.<br><br>Mangle had been a constant problem for many heroes in Paragon until something changed him - no one knows exactly what it was. Now he roams the Rogue Isles, looking to take down those who spread corruption - no matter the cost. <br><br> His current plan to take down Johnny Sonata at the cost of all of St. Martial should show just how far he's willing to go."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1330238172" "The magic that I found should stay strong. Now it's just a matter of finding more Wailers..."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1443113862" "{HeroName}, huh? I've heard of you, and I know what you deserve - the same fate as Johnny Sonata! Lucky for me that you've come straight to me to have it done."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3532283424" "I'm serving true justice here, something YOU could never understand!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3458722486" "I will NOT take any chances with this!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3390905819" "Justice at any cost, {HeroName}. At any cost! Why don't you understand?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3822647839" "I'm not going to just sit here while people like Sonata continue to get away with whatever they want!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4095276573" "Does no one truly...understand?"

