"P28576054" "I saw the weirdest thing the other day. A Wailer was riding one of those big Devouring Earth when suddenly the monster grabbed the Wailer and ATE it!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL6-7_Task_09 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1323771710" "These artifacts must be fairly powerful if someone like Darrin Wade is looking for them. Too bad the person who was hired on to get the artifacts lost this list.<br><br> This can always be an opportunity for you, however. You can find the exact location of where the Circle is keeping those artifacts and steal them for yourself - before Wade has a chance to know what happens."
// AcceptString :
"P4022915344" "Steal the Circle of Thorns' artifacts!"
// SendOffString :
"P3488332274" "You head off to take those artifacts for yourself. Maybe if things go <i>really</i> well, Darrin Wade will get those fake artifacts. It could be a fun sight to see them blow up in his face."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3545348166" "Steal the Circle's Artifacts!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2604972404" "Maybe an artifact blowing up in his face will make Wade a little less smug."
// TaskTitle :
"P3639472475" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P567301526" "At this point, the city of Oranbega isn't really too unfamiliar to you. Unfortunately, from the sounds nearby, the Rikti are pretty familiar with this place as well."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1704460352" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've salvaged the raided lair of the Circle and walked away with a good haul. The best part might be thwarting Darrin Wade's own plans in order to further your own. Now it's just deciding if you should keep it to yourself or show off a bit to the ex-Midnighter."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4245072758" "Prime Goal: Retrieve Circle Items"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1088919523" "Eliminate: {HeroName}?"

