"P2424832425" "I saw some Circle of Thorns beating up the Rikti outside of a cave the other day. Something about taking back what was theirs."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_09 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Belinda 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P803948442" "Artifact Enchantment"
// DetailString :
"P2721561922" "You found a note in the chest regarding the artifacts. It says that a woman named Mistress Belinda has enchanted them so that instead of exploding when they're used, they'll explode when they're taken out of the warehouse. You'll have to find her to remove the enchantment!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ItsaTrap 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3580949090" "We've Got You Now"
// DetailString :
"P1370066686" "Belinda fell to the ground, laughing. The Carnival Mask slipped off of her, revealing that it was not one of the usual ones that the Carnies use. <color Violet><br><br>We've got you now, {HeroName}. The enchantment was a fake! Longbow is here now to make sure opportunists like you get put away for a long time!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2812954162" "Darrin Wade has a reputation of using people to his own end - could be why he's not part of the Midnighter Club anymore. Though he <i>also</i> has a reputation for paying very well. If this note is true, the duplicate artifacts are so spot on that it would be too difficult for anyone to tell that they're different - until the final moment. <br><br> Getting these duplicate artifacts for Wade will earn you some cash, and also prevent him from whatever he may be planning next."
// AcceptString :
"P1940919502" "Get the duplicate artifacts for Darrin Wade!"
// SendOffString :
"P3462813566" "Of course the only downside to this plan is having to deal with the Carnival of Shadows. You'll have to make sure to get the smell of evil harlequins off of the artifacts before you give them to Wade."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3256911072" "Steal the Duplicate Artifacts!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4039173370" "You'll have to figure out a way to get a picture of Darrin Wade when the artifacts blow up in his face."
// TaskTitle :
"P2607512498" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1421844173" "The rave music is pounding, though there doesn't seem to be too many Carnies at this specific club."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P321481737" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Darrin Wade's Wish List</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>After defeating the Longbow ambush, you informed Darrin Wade that you had the artifacts. He arrived shortly after to collect and gave you the payment requested - he wasn't able to tell at all that these were fake artifacts. This should be something interesting to remember down the line."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3647735531" "Wait, the artifact will still blow up in someone's face when they use it?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P557809695" "Yeah, it's meant to be a failsafe if anyone gets away."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P213617486" "Do you think we'll be able to really pull this off?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3222337166" "We nabbed four others with this. Why not one more?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2991497367" "Officer Snyder"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4292128452" "Make sure to neutralize {HeroName}. It'll be the fifth one we get today with these artifacts."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1735802188" "There's {HeroName}! Let's get number five!"

