// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PolarShift 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3727170281" "Polar Shift's Use"
// DetailString :
"P1951479099" "You see an image of the woman known as Polar Shift.<br><br>A voice echoes in your mind... <br><br><color VioletRed>Polar Shift...a woman who has lost her sanity. Her grip on reality is slowly slipping - the ideals she once believed in are becoming more and more distant. Her path to darkness will be a swift one, requiring no external push. She will eventually yearn for the destruction of everything around her."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SkyDragon 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2363976898" "Sky Dragon's Struggle"
// DetailString :
"P3497384179" "You see an image of the man known as Sky Dragon.<br><br>A voice echoes in your mind... <br><br><color VioletRed>Sky Dragon...a man tasked with protecting Paragon City using the teaching of his old masters. He has struggled with the sheer power that is at his fingertips. He has been shackled, commanded to use them in a proper way...but he is finding more often that his own desires outweigh that of his former master.<br><br>He fights the darkness within himself...but yet finds himself using it for his own ends. It is not known what this man's fate will be - for good or for evil. It would take...another force to help push him towards the...proper path."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Mangle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2571181584" "The Darkness of Mangle"
// DetailString :
"P3485351193" "You see an image of the creature called Mangle.<br><br>A voice echoes in your mind... <br><br><color VioletRed>Mangle...a man rejected by fate, or so he would believe. Outcast by everyone he has cared for, Mangle seeks only the complete dominion of all around him. This man...this creature's possibilities are limitless. <br><br>He has forsaken the world and seeks to do everything in his power to twist it into the world that only he would live in. Mangle seeks nothing but total dominion over the world."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Bocor 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1713819729" "A Priceless Name?"
// DetailString :
"P1743520105" "You opened the chest, expecting some sort of priceless artifact, only to discover a small note inside of it. The note simply had the name a man. There is no indication as to who exactly this name belongs to. You have to wonder why exactly Mr. Bocor went through all the effort to get this small piece of paper. "

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3458949083" "You track down the source of the ritual to a Circle of Thorns lair in the caverns beneath Cap au Diable. You use your contacts to discover why exactly Mr. Bocor was interested in Olivia Starr in the first place - her soul had been marked as a doorway between planes. <br><br>When this ritual is complete, a doorway will be temporarily unlocked to a plane called the 'Ether Plane', where it is said that great power and knowledge sit, waiting for someone to come and take it. That someone is going to be you - if you get to the portal first."
// AcceptString :
"P4041255383" "Travel to the next plane before Bocor!"
// SendOffString :
"P864998934" "You call in some favors from contacts and others that you know within the Isles - they'll keep Bocor busy while you're looting this plane for everything that it has. If Bocor does show up in the end, you'll be sure to show him just how you feel about <color red>others getting in your way.</color>"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P766995769" "Plunder the Ether Plane!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2170518644" "You've got to hurry to the planar portal before Bocor gets there.  Time is of the essence."
// TaskTitle :
"P923666220" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Long Line of Spirits</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P532311076" "You step onto the 'Ether Plane'. Knowledge on it is very limited - all you know is that great power <i>should</i> await somewhere within."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4251922797" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Long Line of Spirits</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step out from the Ether Plane with less than what you thought you would get. You'll have to look into the reason why Mr. Bocor would go through all this trouble just for a piece of paper with a name on it - perhaps finding out the reason will lead to something useful."
// Script Variable OBJECT_DISPLAYNAME :
"P547549941" "Seal of the Ether"
// Script Variable OBJECT_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3859849464" "This is the last seal between our plane and the plane of the Ether. Once it is broken, the treasures of the plane will be ripe for the picking."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - EtherSeal 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P4028367571" "You have destroyed the Seal of the Ether."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P990478317" "The seal has been broken! We are free! Free! Time to KILL!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2225393312" "The bloodlust shall finally be fulfilled!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1628416996" "Too long, too long to be kept here!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P240454798" "Feast! Feast, for the time has finally arrived!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1349075135" "Ohhhh, I want some flesh to KILL!"

