// RandomFameString :
"P3538076808" "Did you notice Mr. Bocor in Port Oakes? I never thought I would say this, but he looks...kinda nervous! I wonder why?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SoulSaving 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2872924225" "Olivia Starr's Soul"
// DetailString :
"P2586526013" "You ripped Olivia Starr's soul away from the Circle mage. The bright ball of energy swirled around you happily, giving you the information needed to access all of her bank accounts - within the Rogue Isles and also around the world. Once you took down this information, her soul floated away to an unknown destination."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3666152368" "<color orange>Mr. Bocor tips his hat to you, bowing his head slightly.</color><br><br>{HeroName}, welcome. It would appear you have freed the soul of my dear acquaintance. Very...well done, on your part. I must ask, however...what would drive you to do this? To get in the way of <i>my</i> affairs?"
// Answer Text :
"P226622875" "Nothing personal, Bocor. This was just a business deal."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3469459800" "<color orange>Mr. Bocor leans back, running his hand along the rim of his hat.</color><br><br>Ah...a matter of money. I see. I must convey to you the nature of the situation, {HeroName}. You have disrupted a ceremony that I have spent some time to form. Everything was perfectly orchestrated to lead to this moment.<br><br>And yet...here you are. An agent of chaos, as it would be, stomping in here to ruin everything I've worked so hard to accomplish.<br><br>Now the question is...what should I <i>do</i> with you?"
// Answer Text :
"P3841800039" "I told you this was business, Bocor. Don't make it more than that."
// Page Business Text :
"P1967066273" "<color orange>Mr. Bocor's face shows the slightest hint of a scowl, some dark energy forming around his feet.</color><br><br>My...friend. This may be business for you, but this was <i>quite</i> personal for me. It is quite unfortunate that leaving you alive at this point is <i>not an option</i>."
// Answer Text :
"P2980070578" "Mind if I put in a quick word?"
// Answer Text :
"P2759011033" "(Punch Bocor so hard in the face that his Vodoun ancestors will feel it!)"
// Page QuickWord Text :
"P744403584" "I suppose giving you one last word is only fair. What is it? <br><br><color orange>You explain to Bocor that you have just fought through a small army of demons and cultists to get here and that he shouldn't even begin to question what you've fought before these Circle lackeys. You finish by gesturing to Bocor that he should back down from you right now, unless he wants to retrieve that hat of his from a rather unpleasant place."
// Answer Text :
"P3485035465" "Are we clear now?"
// Page Crystal Text :
"P1218977813" "...crystal.<br><br><color orange>Mr. Bocor nods slowly to you before walking away.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1419158355" "That's one way to handle a Vodoun priest."
// Page WHAM Text :
"P269035160" "<color orange>Mr. Bocor falls to the ground, his hat flying off his head, the glasses on his face cracking in half. He seems to be down for the count.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2124170873" "Tell your ancestors I said hello."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3550558054" "Normally you wouldn't be too concerned about the predicament of Olivia Starr - but the fact that she's throwing a very large amount of money to anyone who is willing to help her out <i>does</i> go a long way towards changing your mind.<br><br>Bocor most likely has some goons within the Circle of Thorns running the ritual, which means you'll have to bust in there and stop them before Olivia's soul - and the information for her bank account - is lost."
// AcceptString :
"P1852448252" "Save Olivia Starr's soul!"
// SendOffString :
"P728461287" "You receive word from one of your contacts that the system of caves that the Circle is in <i>actually</i> starts all the way in St. Martial. Looks like you're in for a bit of a walk."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1008585442" "If Olivia Starr tries to trick you with this, you'll be sure to somehow find where her soul goes and make her living afterlife hell."
// TaskTitle :
"P1441103067" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Long Line of Spirits</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3918987835" "After nearly an eternity of walking, you arrive at the cavern where the Circle should be, deep beneath the island of Cap au Diable."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3595230342" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Long Line of Spirits</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to free Olivia Starr, get all the information on her bank accounts, <i>and</i> put Mr. Bocor in his place. Looks like you won't have to worry too much about him retaliating - if he knows what's good for him."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2583086703" "Why have we agreed to help Bocor out?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3829463925" "He claims that we shall be given full access to the Ether Plane - he only wishes for a small item within it."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1635800801" "It seems, in the end, we all gained access to Starr."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P273376952" "If only we had known of Bocor's plans earlier, back during our operations in Oakes."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1511555952" "Soul Carrier"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1313839775" "Her soul is safely in our grasp. We shall begin the ritual right away."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P944152874" "Ah...{HeroName}. And here we believed this would be...easy."

