"P4126474271" "Word on the street is that Mr. Bocor is furious at {HeroName}. I wonder why?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL6-7_Task_11 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3169288060" "Those heroes within Paragon are always waiting for the chance to spring into action to rescue any sort of damsel in distress. Such predictable behavior is excellent for someone such as yourself to use to your advantage - which you fully intend to do."
// AcceptString :
"P1721823724" "Trick some heroes into the sewers of St. Martial!"
// SendOffString :
"P2643773717" "You've got your plan all set in motion. You'll have to first make sure to silence the girl hiding in the sewers - you can't risk the heroes <i>actually</i> finding her. Next you'll release a fake broadcast, disguising your voice. Then all you'll have to do is sit back and let the heroes come straight to you - for their beating, of course."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P60099432" "Fool some heroes!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P386079098" "What heroes might show up to save the day?"
// TaskTitle :
"P922592505" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Krazy Mark's KRAZY DEALS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2992210279" "These sewers are crawling with Wailer demons - which is fine. All you're looking for is that woman."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P457766633" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Krazy Mark's KRAZY DEALS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You should start keeping count of all the heroes you've taken out - the list is starting to grow too long to keep track of. <br><br>Though it was a bit of an upset that some of the supers you handled weren't true heroes just yet."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3852592679" "Liiiisaaa!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2011169130" "She's a nice catch, aaaawooo!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4084726369" "Johnny wants youse demons DONE!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_TWO_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2781211736" "Awooo! Johnny's gonna burn!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ONE_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1817672425" "Family Mook"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2659497014" "You demons got a lotta freakin' nerve showin' up here!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P533787029" "Themari wants her back, but we can use her better!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P867495980" "Ohhhh baby you know!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P941540531" "Johnny ain't gonna hold us back for much longer with Liisa Liiiisa!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P96429622" "Lisa Darls"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P305554919" "This demon seems to be the woman that Peter Themari is looking for - though you guess that she probably wasn't like this before Themari got his hands on her."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2012700615" "What...what has happened to me?! I used to be beautiful! I used to be different! I used...I used to be a human!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2900283871" "I see that violent look in your eye {HeroName}...I will NOT let you corner me here!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Lisa 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1326398336" "Silence Lisa Darls!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Computer 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ModelDisplayName :
"P1017077819" "Communicator"
// Description :
"P3806627485" "Find a communicator to put in the fake distress call!"
// InteractCompleteString :
"P1209277963" "You've put in the call - now to wait for the heroes to wade in!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1556203445" "<shout>Don't worry Lisa, we're here to get you outta here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3860403822" "Wh - {HeroName}?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2206795696" "This...this isn't what it looks like! I'm just doing this for the money, I swear!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P912969942" "Ugh! Why am I lying to YOU?! I'm doing this because I WANT to help her, okay?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2379305213" "You're not going to get away with this!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P1746075174" "You won't...stop this...!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Thystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3625699231" "Defeat Miss Thystle!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2641154310" "Flambeaux"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3540470928" "<shout>This'll be fun! Rescue the girl, BLOW up the Giza, and then burn Themari! Everyone'll hear about it!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3570304379" "{HeroName}? Oh this is PERFECT! You're a MUCH bigger catch than Themari!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2694674399" "If I burn you to a crisp, that'll get everyone's attention! I'll be Flambeaux, burner of {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2123971219" "<em flex2> Impressed yet, {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3203625219" "Ow! You're not staying down!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P1810914354" "Huh...?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Flam 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2634002070" "Defeat Flambeaux!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1992127588" "Frostfire"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P85175475" "<shout>No one else dies today, not on my watch. Themari won't get that girl if I have anything to say about it."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3998252636" "{HeroName}? So... This is a trap is it?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2254661720" "You'll have to excuse me if I flip this trap around on you. Get {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3086476074" "I'm a changed man, {HeroName}. The kind of man who is going to stop scum like you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3514538309" "I couldn't even...save this one person..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Frostfire 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1068007239" "Defeat Frostfire!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable ACTOR_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2054855881" "<shout>We've got a location on {HeroName}, move move move!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2127793960" "You've finished off the heroes! Maybe next time they'll know better, though if they did, it would ruin some of your fun."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P4014604854" "I saw Frostfire the other day and he was seething! I wouldn't want to get on his bad side, that's for sure."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_11 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Lisa 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P838138232" "Cracked Rune"
// DetailString :
"P987301205" "A large burst of magic filled the sewers, causing your protective rune against the Wailers to shatter instantly!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - HollowPoint 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3915062409" "Hollow Point's Rule"
// DetailString :
"P784227271" "You found some notes off of one of the Circle of Thorns. You read them over to see they contain a discussion regarding Hollow Point, who may become a major factor within the Isles. They say that he is gathering the resources to form his own army, possibly looking to either take over one of the islands in the Isles - or to possibly utilize one of the unpopulated islands offshore of the Isles.<br><br>The Circle and Themari seem to be wary of him and have plans to take him down, should Hollow Point become too dangerous for their liking."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2186299092" "<color orange>You see what appears to be a succubus...cowering in fear...?</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P293833389" "Er...Lisa...Darls...?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1715954343" "<color orange>The succubus startles, leaping away from you, assuming a combat stance. She calms for a moment, sighing heavily.</color><br><br>Y-you know my name? What do you want?! Are you here from Themari?! Who are you?!"
// Answer Text :
"P2289765983" "The name's {HeroName}, and no, I'm here to get you out of here...for a price."
// Page Business Text :
"P3759321098" "<color orange>Lisa's face brightens as she straightens her posture.</color><br><br>Thank goodness! Oh, I'll pay you anything, you name it! Just get me out of here! Themari...he's changed me.<br><br>I used to be normal...I used to be a beautiful woman! Now look at me! I'm some sort of monster! And for what?! For his amusement? So he can say he turned someone into a demon?!<br><br>You can't let him get me again, you can't!"
// Answer Text :
"P221410555" "Calm down. You've got the money, so you've got my services."
// Answer Text :
"P443140474" "Whoa - whoa - easy there. Not here for a life story... Just here for the money, lady."
// Page QuickWord Text :
"P1425000444" "Right...right...of course. I'll give you the information for one of my bank accounts now, and the rest once you get me out of here.<br><br>Themari, he's sure to be looking for me! I can feel him getting closer and closer...w-wait...what was that?!<br><br><color orange>A large burst of magic flies through the sewers. You can feel the protective rune shatter into pieces."
// Answer Text :
"P3725539193" "...that's not good."
// Page Crystal Text :
"P2865062271" "It's Themari! He's here! {HeroName}, you have to handle him! I-I'll meet you outside once he's gone. I can't let him get me again - I WON'T!<br><br><color orange>Lisa quickly leaps away, finding a place to hide.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P293920270" "One day, -one- day this will be simple."
// Page WHAM Text :
"P2101972025" "<color orange>Lisa Darls sighs, taking a breath.</color><br><br>You're right. I'm sorry...you don't care about any of that. I should be grateful that you're here to help me. We can arrange the form of payment once I get out of here.<br><br><color orange>Suddenly, a large burst of magic flies through the sewers. You can feel the protective rune shatter into pieces. Lisa Darls startles, looking about.</color><br><br>What was that?!"
// Answer Text :
"P110737609" "I'm guessing that was Themari and his friends. They're not happy."
// Page NotHappy Text :
"P2349011894" "You have to stop them! I'm not going back to Themari, he won't take me! <br><br><color orange>Lisa Darls quickly leaps away to hide, leaving you to deal with the current situation.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1621991678" "Oh don't mind me! It's not like you're now a powerful DEMON or anything!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Themari 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2791256017" "<color orange>Peter Themari smiles, bearing his green, rotted teeth.</color><br><br>Ah...{HeroName}. What a surprise to find you here. I trust you're doing well?"
// Answer Text :
"P1771248980" "Themari, I'm really certain that you're not surprised to see me."
// Answer Text :
"P1679633357" "Are you seriously asking me that question?"
// Answer Text :
"P3329888221" "Oh yeah, I just had to handle a few lackeys of some goon. How about you?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1047197352" "Hah.<br><br>Yes, I suppose you're correct. It's most upsetting that you've chosen to try to save Miss Darls. I assume you've seen the work I've done on her?<br><br>She has the body of a monster, but still lacks the will of one. My project is still only halfway done - I will have her perfected, at least better than that Pyriss girl.<br><br>At any rate, it seems you currently stand in my way."
// Answer Text :
"P681310081" "Looks to be that way. Which means you have a very big problem."
// Page BigProblem Text :
"P3318060646" "<color orange>Peter Themari lets out a deep laugh, his breath smelling like ash.</color><br><br>No my friend, I believe <i>you</i> are the one who has the problem. Unlike many of my...cohorts in the Isles, I am <i>fully</i> capable of handling a situation, should I need to."
// Answer Text :
"P1179758568" "You're welcome to try, Themari."
// Page Welcome Text :
"P14386072" "<color orange>Themari's eyes light up with a bright fire before he vanishes in a burst of smoke!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1371355053" "Here we go..."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1785522078" "Why not? I always believe in showing some proper manners. Especially to someone who you're going to wipe off of this mortal coil."
// Answer Text :
"P3387570545" "No one seems to understand the idea of 'business'. That's all this is."
// Page JustBusiness Text :
"P763430325" "Of course, {HeroName}, I understand business quite well.<br><br>But your business happens to conflict with mine. Which is why one of us cannot be allowed to succeed."
// Answer Text :
"P199469764" "I'm assuming this isn't the part where you walk away peacefully."
// Page WalkAway Text :
"P829499686" "No. It - is - NOT!<br><br><color orange>Peter Themari bellows before he vanishes in a cloud of smoke."
// Answer Text :
"P352363378" "...great."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3998715076" "<color orange>Themari's eye twitches in irritation as he grits his teeth together.</color><br><br>I'm just - FINE - {HeroName}. Especially considering that I am here to see to some unfinished business."
// Answer Text :
"P316117064" "Your teeth won't get any cleaner by being in a sewer, you know."
// Page Teeth Text :
"P167188833" "<color orange>Themari rubs his arm along his lips, glaring at you.</color><br><br>You're just full of jokes, aren't you, {HeroName}?"
// Answer Text :
"P949596629" "I always try to enjoy myself when making money."
// Page MakingMoney Text :
"P2970592859" "Enough of your ramblings!<br><br><color orange>Peter Themari bellows before he vanishes in a cloud of smoke."
// Answer Text :
"P3976614053" "Just when I thought we were getting along..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1777433772" "You do some digging on the identity of Lisa Darls to find out she's actually a <i>very</i> wealthy stock market broker with a large amount of expensive stocks - which can be yours, if you help her out of this situation.<br><br>If she's underneath the sewers in St. Martial, it'll mean she's in Wailer territory. Fighting through those Wailers will be sure to startle the woman into running away - which could lead to her into more danger. That's not something you can risk. You'll have to figure out a way to placate the wailers in order to safely reach the Lisa Darls - if you choose to help her."
// AcceptString :
"P288189539" "Save Lisa Darls!"
// SendOffString :
"P2883681752" "You put in the request to a few of your contacts that you require a method of walking past Wailers untouched. One of your more reliable contacts sends you a magical rune. They say that it will make the Wailers think you're one of their own, so long as you hold onto it. Though the contact <i>did</i> warn you that the rune was very sensitive and could be shattered easily.<br><br>This'll have to do for now."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4092278381" "Hopefully you'll get there before Peter Themari can claim his prize again."
// TaskTitle :
"P2740824355" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Krazy Mark's KRAZY DEALS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3704676068" "You passed by some Wailers in the sewers - none of them seemed to even notice you. That should make this task of getting Lisa Darls nice and easy."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2106519162" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Krazy Mark's KRAZY DEALS!</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You're not too terribly surprised that took more effort than you imagined. Lisa Darls gave you all the information needed to access her bank account.<br><br> You watched as she ran off into the streets of St. Martial. She's avoided Themari for now, though how much longer she has is anyone's guess."

