// RandomFameString :
"P3799277867" "I could have sworn that I saw an Arachnos flier zip out of Dark Astoria earlier.  Why would anyone want to set foot in there?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_12 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P324508139" "While stealing Sky Dragon's items and selling them on the black market <i>is</i> tempting, you probably wouldn't be able to fetch much money for them, given that whoever obtains them will be hunted down like a dog by Sky Dragon and beaten into a pulp. Now...this <i>other</i> job, however, with Amanda Vines, can be profitable. Marshal Brass has been known to work together with freelancers from time to time - albeit <i>work together</i> might be a bit much, as he usually shows a great deal of disdain in asking for hired help.<br><br>If something were to...happen to that Arachnos squad going to rescue Vines, he'd have no choice but to pay you for her rescue."
// AcceptString :
"P416852778" "Force your way into saving Amanda Vines!"
// SendOffString :
"P1591497871" "You swiftly make your way to where Sky Dragon is holding Amanda Vines, making sure to let the Arachnos squad get there first - after all, you'll have to make it look like someone other than <i>you</i> took them out."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3634972373" "Rescue Amanda Vines!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P961135377" "Maybe you'll use some of your money towards the medical bills for these Arachnos soldiers."
// TaskTitle :
"P1332283510" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Dr. Aeon's Science Convention</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1923004278" "This must be the place where Sky Dragon is keeping Amanda Vines. First things first - handling that squad of Arachnos."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P746371691" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Dr. Aeon's Science Convention</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You contact Marshal Brass regarding payment for rescuing Vines - after Brass discovers that the 'RIP' took down his squad, he is all but eager to pay you - for both rescuing Vines and for keeping quiet about the matter."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P9927255" "One day I'm going to rise to the top, THEN Marshal Brass will regret ever crossing me! <em t=12> Then what's the point of all of this? If we work hard enough, we'll get there."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3252360106" "Hah! Yeah, right. <em t=8>Don't you understand? You'll never get to the top. None of us ever will. <em t=4> You're fooling yourself. Just keep your head down and you won't get hurt."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3895596979" "Now you've done it...!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2836457115" "Now you die!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Arachnos 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3797305502" "Take out the Arachnos patrol!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3563698646" "You've knocked out the Arachnos patrol. Now to get Amanda Vines!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P11715777" "Is it really a good idea to be working with this guy?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1523253296" "I don't make the calls around here, just keep your mouth shut!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1606676939" "I'm surprised this guy doesn't seem to, well, you know, CARE too much about some of what we've done."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P155333981" "Sky Dragon only cares about getting the job done. We just gotta make sure we're not dead when that happens."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2429964273" "Is this going to work?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2925663911" "It better, it won't look good for us if Vines escapes."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P2905786540" "Amanda Vines"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3366507403" "Amanda Vines is the star reporter for WPSDR, though it seems she has once again gotten in over her head."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3188009376" "Let go of me! You're all going to be in tomorrow night's broadcast! Corruption in the RIP!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P947446931" "{HeroName}...! He was right...get out of here! Run!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2089617329" "Shut up! We've seen the other pieces you've done on us - you think we care anymore?"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4138791311" "There's {HeroName}! Do it!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P309259425" "Police Captain"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P3709947183" "{HeroName}, Sky Dragon was never doing any project! He set this up to lure you into an ambush!"

