// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P740878047" "You should be honored, {HeroName}, that I went through all this effort to lure you out!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P295526315" "Everything worked out perfectly. I knew Arachnos would send someone in to save Vines, and I knew YOU would take advantage of that!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3298430275" "You're more powerful than I previously predicted, it seems..."
