// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Swan 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P885378643" "<color orange>Swan seems to be completely unconscious for the moment."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Numina 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P228153385" "<color orange>Numina seems to be knocked out, her spirit fading in and out from view..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3547250007" "Psymon's predicament will provide you with ample opportunities - mainly organizing the potential for a massive psychic explosion throughout all of Nerva! The amount of harm this will cause is massive - ranging from Longbow in Agincourt, to Crey, to the Circle of Thorns...<br><br>You'll have to get your hands on some Longbow communicators in order to radio in some of the big name psychics to come to Nerva as soon as possible. Then, it's a matter of sitting back and watching the chaos ensue - provided you have something to shield yourself from the explosion."
// AcceptString :
"P3987788262" "Cause a psychic explosion!"
// SendOffString :
"P1592615170" "You do some investigating to discover a piece of Crey technology that will give the user temporary invulnerability to psychic shockwaves - you plan on activating this right before the main event, as the device will only work once. You wouldn't want to be knocked out with everyone else, of course."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P969924225" "Trigger the Psychic Explosion!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2526701066" "You'll have to figure out what you'll do when you're the last person standing in Nerva Archipelago - at least for some time..."
// TaskTitle :
"P2997394545" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mind Splitting Headache</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2633150415" "You arrive in Nerva, where Longbow are doing their patrols. Time to enact your plan!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1541274362" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mind Splitting Headache</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You walk away from the main square in Nerva, leaving all of the various people caught in your wake there. Nerva, even if it was for one brief moment, was entirely locked down, thanks to the problems of Psymon Omega.<br><br>The best part? Those in positions of authority are looking to go after <i>him</i> now for the incident - you were able to cause this amount of chaos <i>and</i> get away with it!"
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P1756859898" "Penelope Yin"
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P368479866" "Swan"
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P1575607881" "Numina"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2390476940" "Aaaaagh!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2166634987" "Communication Officer"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P461024526" "Get Liberty on the radio, we've got a serious problem here! Did we find the source yet?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P837141082" "It's {HeroName}! We prepared for this!"

