"P1813263320" "You send an SOS to Penelope Yin, requesting her presence in Nerva as soon as possible."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P63372971" "Ugh...this headache is killing me! Isn't there something to stop this?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1112896952" "It's {HeroName}! Find out how {Hero.gender=Male he|she} doesn't have a headache!"

