"P1391532917" "Uhhh...I hit my head really hard in Nerva before...I don't even know how long I was out for. What happened...?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL6-7_Task_13 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Honoree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1083350201" "Search for the Honoree"
// DetailString :
"P1594895761" "Deep within the Rikti base, you found some interesting information off of a Rikti terminal. It was hard to figure out what most of the data said, though one thing did stand out - the Rikti in the base were ordered to search for the location of someone called the 'Honoree'."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Device 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P684537601" "The Psychic Disruptor"
// DetailString :
"P3346698343" "You found the device that controls the psychic disruptor, which would appear to be the machine that the Rikti are using to cause Psymon Omega all these problems.<br><br>You're able to figure out what must be done in order to stop the machine - time to see if Psymon is willing to pay up."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1197341843" "<color orange>You adjust the oddly convenient radio in this Rikti base to try to pick up Psymon Omega. After a few tries, you hear his angry voice yell over the speakers.</color><br><br>Who is this?! I am in a VERY bad mood right now so this better be GOOD!"
// Answer Text :
"P2917069167" "Hello Psymon, I'm here to discuss the situation you're currently in..."
// Answer Text :
"P70528733" "Would you consider an end to your problems 'good'?"
// Answer Text :
"P3200823845" "I was just calling you about stopping your little problem. But if you're in a bad mood..."
// Page Nothing Text :
"P3465995827" "<color orange>This two-way radio is silent.</color>"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3826009938" "Oh? And what exactly would you like to <i>discuss</i> about it?! The extreme pain or the UNCONTROLLABLE pain?!"
// Answer Text :
"P2985883388" "Actually, the part about ending the pain."
// Page EndPain Text :
"P1943631419" "Wait...<br><br>Are you telling me you can somehow stop the pain I'm in? Are you the person behind all of this? I swear I will hunt you down! I am <i>Psymon Omega</i>! Is this the work of that dog, Romulus?"
// Answer Text :
"P4144348149" "(Explain the scenario to Psymon)"
// Page Explain Text :
"P1841134118" "I...I see.<br><br>Well...bravo, {HeroName}, bravo. You certainly have me in quite the predicament. I know when I am defeated, however...so I shall make this deal with you.<br><br>I shall wire you the money you wish - and I shall also pay you some more to keep this little...transaction between the two of us.<br><br>How does that strike you?"
// Answer Text :
"P539878519" "Strikes me just fine, Psymon. Let's make this a deal."
// Page Makeadeal Text :
"P1410865545" "And...there. You will find the appropriate money in your accounts.<br><br><color orange>You push a button to destroy the psychic disruptor, ending Psymon Omega's pain.</color><br><br>Ah...you're a lifesaver, {HeroName}. Pleasure doing business with you."
// Answer Text :
"P3477087647" "You as well, Psymon."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3441709400" "An end to my pro - <br><br>Are you saying you have a way to end my problems?!"
// Answer Text :
"P810661902" "You could say that. First, let's talk money."
// Page TalkMoney Text :
"P2233618143" "I'll give you whatever you want, name it! Psymon Omega is a man with vast wealth and riches!<br><br>Just solve this problem for me already!"
// Answer Text :
"P4108789262" "(Name your price to Psymon Omega)"
// Page PriceIsRight Text :
"P4278894803" "<color orange>Psymon stammers over the pricetag before speaking once more.</color><br><br>Fine! It's done! I'll wire it right away, just do whatever you have to do to stop this!"
// Answer Text :
"P2244329405" "(Shut down the Psychic Disruptor) How's that?"
// Page ShutDown Text :
"P2924842574" "Ahhh...much better. MUCH better.<br><br>I won't forget this, {HeroName}. Psymon Omega does not forget it when someone aids him. You have yourself an excellent day."
// Answer Text :
"P1581198646" "See you around, Psymon."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1509257123" "<color orange>You lower the receiving volume on the communicator to trick Psymon into thinking the signal is being shut off. Psymon frantically yells into the radio.</color><br><br>Just hold on a moment! I did not...!<br><br>Ahem.<br><br>Now...I did not say <i>anything</i> about being too busy to speak about the issue at hand..."
// Answer Text :
"P2520836572" "Huh, well, good to hear! So, I can shut this off for you...if you've got the money!"
// Page Coy Text :
"P1865488045" "<color orange>Psymon mumbles for a moment.</color><br><br>...fine! Ahem...I mean to say...I think we can come to some sort of arrangement. Name your price."
// Answer Text :
"P2931569458" "(Name your price to Psymon)"
// Page Haggle Text :
"P2075654335" "Hrm...<br><br>I'll give you <i>half</i> of that amount. Let's not kid ourselves...{HeroName}, was it?"
// Answer Text :
"P2288275276" "Sorry, I didn't hear you. I found a button here. I think it's Rikti for 'intensify pain'..."
// Page Joke Text :
"P2856588907" "<color orange>Psymon remains silent for a few moments.</color><br><br>I said that we have a deal. I'll wire you the money now."
// Answer Text :
"P4276385323" "Great! It's good that we could come to this arrangement."
// Page Settle Text :
"P3329057751" "It's done, {HeroName}. The amount you requested is in your proper accounts now. I trust that will be all?"
// Answer Text :
"P337923460" "That's just about it! Unless you wanted to give me some more money..."
// Page Blank Text :
"P3710229113" "...goodbye {HeroName}. <br><br><color orange>Psymon Omega shuts off his line of the communicator.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1973078803" "Some people have no sense of humor."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P10674510" "You don't really <i>sympathize</i> with Psymon's plight, but you do see a chance to make some money off of it. You're willing to bet he'd pay anything in order to get his powers back under his control - and probably even more to find out what exactly was the cause of all this. You'll have to do some investigating - and fast - to discover the source of the problem before the potential psychic explosion rocks through Nerva Archipelago."
// AcceptString :
"P448945542" "Sell Psymon the cure to his condition!"
// SendOffString :
"P1689149564" "You trace the cause of Psymon's psychic dilemma to a small cavern in Nerva - there seems to be some pretty impressive technology at work. You'll have to find out whoever is controlling the technology causing these problems for Psymon, then take control of it for yourself. After that, it'll be a simple matter of just ringing up Psymon to determine just how...<i>grateful</i> he would be if you disabled the machinery. Hopefully for his sake he'll be <i>very</i> grateful."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3997153743" "Find the cure for Psymon!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3892139260" "You'll have to figure out just how much money you should ask Psymon to pay for this."
// TaskTitle :
"P1085994761" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mind Splitting Headache</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3002916705" "You enter the cave, though something doesn't feel right. This isn't any ordinary cavern system..."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1295029962" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Mind Splitting Headache</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You emerge from the cavern to a headache-free Nerva Archipelago. And also with a great deal more money in your bank account. All in all, today turned out to be a pretty good day!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P487098042" "Project: Success. Psymon Omega: Near Broken."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3856228713" "{HeroName}: Bothersome"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P738268325" "Psychic Explosion: Imminent"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3079039152" "Psychic Shielding: Online"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3314637277" "{HeroName}: (Censored)"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3906413357" "Love when: plan comes together."

